-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----
<<REPLACE THIS FILE WITH YOUR REAL cosign.pub>>

Generate the keypair locally (see README "cosign setup"):

    cosign generate-key-pair

Commit the resulting cosign.pub OVER this file, and add the matching
cosign.key contents as the COSIGN_PRIVATE_KEY repo secret. NEVER commit
cosign.key. This placeholder intentionally is not a valid key so a
misconfigured pipeline fails loudly instead of silently trusting nothing.
